    "date": "2021-04-13T18:34:44Z",
    "text": "Nuclear Plant Decommissioning Act of 2020\n\nThis bill (1) provides a mechanism for states, tribal and local governments to play a role in the development of post-shutdown decommissioning activities regarding the shutdown of a nuclear facility; and (2) establishes a grant program to support community advisory boards that aim to foster communication between a licensee involved in decommissioning activities and members of a community that may be affected by such activities."
